Welcome back to What I=E2=80=99m Hearing, and Happy New Year to everyone
who survived =E2=80=99til =E2=80=9925. Is it too early to suggest Hollywood=
 will be =E2=80=9Cfixed in =E2=80=9926=E2=80=9D?=C2=A0

