As I mentioned Monday, I=E2=80=99m taking a few days off, and unlike my usu=
al vacations, I=E2=80=99m not holed up in some hotel business center or sea=
rching for WiFi on a mountaintop. I=E2=80=99m actually off and offline (I w=
rote this intro last weekend), back on Monday. Meanwhile, it=E2=80=99s a pe=
rfect opportunity for box office guru Scott
Mendelson to offer his take on both the holiday movie race and the entire y=
ear that was. All yours, Scott=E2=80=A6

2024=E2=80=99s Christmas Box Office Happy Ending

